description: This course is a critical investigation into Australian competition law. The course seeks to develop students' knowledge of the Competition and Consumer Act 2010 (Cth) and ability to solve complex legal problems.
incompatible: LA414 or LW816 or LAWS7138 or 7338
restricted: LLB(Hons)(#64), LLB(Hons)(#48), LLB (Graduate Entry), LLB(Hons) duals and LLB dual programs.
